      <title>Station Access 2 character slot bonus</title>
      <link>http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=Crier&amp;message.id=359#M359</link>
      <description>Starting sometime tomorrow morning the 2 extra character slots everyone currently has available due to subscription server vs login server issues will be reverted back to available only for those with Station Access subscriptions.&amp;nbsp; If you chose to utilize these extra slots and do not currently have a Station Access subscription, none of your characters will be deleted, however the 2 with a name starting with a letter the farthest down the alphabet will be unavailable to you until you delete 2 characters or transfer 2 characters to another server or account.&lt;br&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
