      <description>&lt;p class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;font face="Verdana" size="2"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Verdana;"&gt;On Thursday, September &#xD;
14&lt;sup&gt;th&lt;/sup&gt; from &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face="Verdana" size="2"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Verdana;"&gt;4am&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face="Verdana" size="2"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Verdana;"&gt; to &#xD;
