modifying, creating, and canceling)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt; &#xD;
&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;font face="Verdana" size="2"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Verdana;"&gt;Station Exchange&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt; &#xD;
