      <title>Choose Your Own Adventure</title>
      <link>http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=Crier&amp;message.id=348#M348</link>
      <description>Last year I started writing a story about a young wood elf girl named Kaiya.&amp;nbsp; As the story progressed, 3 or 4 questions were put before the community here to help determine what direction the story took.&amp;nbsp; We made it thru 2 chapters of Kaiya's story before I had to take a break from it.&amp;nbsp; However I decided to start this up again at chapter 3.&amp;nbsp; If you are interested in reading what has occured so far and helping to &lt;a href="http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=Fun&amp;amp;message.id=9539&amp;amp;jump=true" target=_blank&gt;decide Kaiya's fate&lt;/a&gt;, join in on the Just for Fun board.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Please be kind should you read the story and wish to offer feedback, I am in no way a professional writer.&amp;nbsp; &lt;span&gt;:smileyhappy:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
