      <title>House of Commons Dev Chat Logs â€“ August 23, 2006</title>
      <link>http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=Crier&amp;message.id=347#M347</link>
      <description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&#xD;
           &lt;td class="newsTitle" width="99%"&gt;House of&#xD;
  Commons Dev Chat Logs â€“ August 23, 2006&lt;/td&gt;&#xD;
