      <title>Community Member Highlight of the Week</title>
      <link>http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=Crier&amp;message.id=344#M344</link>
      <description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;As many of you already know we highlight a community member every week on EQPlayers.&amp;nbsp; No this is not the same as the player of the day randomly selected each day but something a bit more personal posted on Thursdays on the EQPlayers news site.&amp;nbsp; You can see a sample here - &lt;a href="http://eqplayers.station.sony.com/news_article.vm?id=50203&amp;amp;month=current" target="_blank"&gt;Sample Highlight&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;For the past 6 months or so, the community members highlighted were chosen by invitation, now we are prepared to let anyone participate if they wish.&amp;nbsp; I&lt;b&gt;f you are interested in participating and being selected as a Community Member of the Week, please answer the questionnaire below and email it to me at cdelzer@soe.sony.com with EQ Player Highlight in the subject line.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;You are also welcome to submit a tasteful real life picture and screen shot of your character is you would like to.&amp;nbsp; Feel free to disregard any question in the questionnaire you do not wish to answer.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;NOTE: Highlighted community members are randomly selected from all the available questionnaires I have each week, so you may not see yours immediately upon sending it in.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;We also reserve the right to disregard or edit inappropriately answered questions if necessary however it is much more likley that an inappropriate answer will&amp;nbsp; cause your questionnaire to be disgarded completely, so please follow the same rules for the forums when responding to the questions.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Please submit questionnaires in either notepad or Word format.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;*********************&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Real life first name:&lt;br&gt;Forum handle:&lt;br&gt;Main Character name:&lt;br&gt;Server:&lt;br&gt;Guild:&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Where in the real life world do you live? (city &amp;amp; state or equivalent only please!) &lt;br&gt;How long have you played EQ?&lt;br&gt;What other MMOs have you played?&lt;br&gt;What type of work do you do?&lt;br&gt;How long is your typical gaming session when playing EQ?&lt;br&gt;What does a typical EQ day consist of for you?&lt;br&gt;What was the race and class of your very first character?&lt;br&gt;What got you into gaming and what sort of games do you like the most?&lt;br&gt;What other hobbies or activities do you take part in, other then playing EverQuest? &lt;br&gt;What is your highest level in EQ?&lt;br&gt;What race and class is your main character?&lt;br&gt;What do you like the most about the class you have chosen for your main character?&lt;br&gt;Does your main character worship a deity?&lt;br&gt;How did you choose your main character's name?&lt;br&gt;Which classes in EQ have you NOT played?&lt;br&gt;What is your favorite expansion?&lt;br&gt;What is your favorite zone?&lt;br&gt;What is your favorite npc?&lt;br&gt;Which expansion do you like the least?&lt;br&gt;Which zone do you like the least?&lt;br&gt;Which npc do you like the least?&lt;br&gt;What is the most platinum you have ever spent on purchasing a single item for one of your characters?&lt;br&gt;Do you have an item you no longer use but keep around for nostalgic reasons? If so what is it and why do you keep it?&lt;br&gt;What do you like best about EverQuest?&lt;br&gt;What do you get out of playing EverQuest?&lt;br&gt;Describe your best experience from playing EverQuest?&lt;br&gt;Do you run or work for an EverQuest Fan Site? (if so provide the web address too!)&lt;br&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Message Edited by Kytherea on &lt;span class=date_text&gt;08-17-2006&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=time_text&gt;10:50 AM&lt;/span&gt;</description>
