      <description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;Players in the EverQuest community continue doing amazing things.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Because you guys are so talented and creative, we're going to be having a focus on EverQuest Fan Art!&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;So, if you would like to see some of your creative productions on a web page please send it to us!&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Here's how to submit your EQ Fan Art to us so that we might show off your talented creativity...&lt;br&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br&gt;FAN ART SUBMISSION GUIDELINES:&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;â€¢ Send the image to&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="http://" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Verdana;"&gt;&lt;a href="mailto:soefanart@soe.sony.com" target="_blank"&gt;soefanart@soe.sony.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; and put "EQ Fan Art" in the subject line of your email.&lt;br&gt;â€¢ Be sure to include your Forum Handle, your in-game name and your server in the email.&lt;br&gt;â€¢ The image you send us needs to be one of these formats (.bmp/.jpg/.gif) and should be no bigger than 400k.&amp;nbsp; If you have multiple images you may send them as a .zip which should not exceed 1.5mb.&lt;br&gt;â€¢ Please try to make the images as high quality as possible.&lt;br&gt;â€¢ All material submitted must be reviewed.&amp;nbsp; If we have any questions, we will contact you.&lt;br&gt;â€¢ Please remember to keep a copy for yourself as we do not archive these materials.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;SOE may use, modify, distribute or display any submission, in whole or in part, in its sole and absolute discretion.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Any and all submissions are subject to the &lt;a href="http://help.station.sony.com/cgi-bin/soe.cfg/php/enduser/std_adp.php?p_faqid=15630" target="_blank"&gt;Sony Online Terms of Service&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;NOTE: Once this gets going, you will be directed to submit through a web page and will no longer have to use the above email address or subject title.&amp;nbsp; This request is to start off the project with some of our community members art work.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
